Job Summary

We are looking for Business Intelligence Analyst to manage data visualization and dashboard projects within banking Industry.
Mandatory Skill-set
Degree in Computer Science or Data Analytics or equivalent;
Minimum 4 years of experience in delivering end-to-end data solutions;
Has production knowledge and experience in data modelling and UI development using QlikView/Tableau;
Involved in Data mapping, Data modelling and scripting to support key performance indicators and time comparison;
